channel.title: "Dynasty" 317 or 474 - Combat - Project Insanity
channel.description:
Hello, I am working on a server named "Dynasty". I don't really care what deob it is, but I'm sticking with either 474 or 317. It will be a Project Insanity source until we find something better. Stuff I've changed- -Took out all custom items. -Took out all custom npc's. -Fixed doors. -Fixed some commands. -Fixed up client. (Renamed everything to Dynasty) -Relocated shops, moved into the edgeville bank. -Relocated home, now at edgeville. -Relocated death spawn, now a little south of edgeville. What I'm going to do- -Take out fire flames in the client. -Add a background. -Make a webclient of my own. Can't think of much more. Application: [code] Name: Age: Can you code?: If you can't code, then can you host the server?: Do you have a msn?: Do you have a microphone?: Are you going to be committed?: Do you have PayPal money?: [/code] Also, we will be using Ventrilo as a communication program. Here's some images of gameplay; [img]http://img821.imageshack.us/i/homecc.png/[/img] [img]http://img695.imageshack.us/i/shopzonebankarea.png/[/img] [img]http://img59.imageshack.us/i/theivingareamoney.png/[/img] If you're interested, reply to this thread with your application, or contact me on msn @
anthonydukaj@live.com
Thanks, Anthony
